Company Overview of MAK Capital One, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
MAK Capital One, LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It manages separate client focused portfolios. The firm invests in the public equity, fixed income, and alternative investment markets. It also employs event driven investing to make its investments. MAK Capital One, LLC was founded in May 2002 and is based in New York City.


