 MAK CAPITAL ONE LLC Overview



												   Mak Capital One Llc is a hedge fund that manages 574.6 MM dollars in regulatory AUM and has 11 employees, of which 6 perform investment advisory functions. The manager's has disclosed holdings from 12/31/06 to 03/31/17. The fund's latest filing disclosed 102MM in positions, representing 18% of the manager's regulatory AUM.
												



